{"id":965,"parent_id":964,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":965,"title":"Malachi 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"Mal.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1","content":[["div",[".title",["span.dominant","Malachi"]],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","The Jews despise the Lord by offering polluted bread upon the altar and by sacrificing animals with blemishes—The Lord’s name will be great among the Gentiles."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.1","order":"02.40.001.63371"},["b","1"],"The burden of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"word"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"to Israel by Malachi."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.2","order":"02.40.001.63372"},["b","2"],"I have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"loved"],"you, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],". Yet ye say, Wherein hast thou loved us?",["i","Was"],"not Esau Jacob’s brother? saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": yet I",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"loved"],"Jacob,"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.3","order":"02.40.001.63373"},["b","3"],"And I hated Esau, and laid his mountains and his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"heritage"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"waste"],"for the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"dragons"],"of the wilderness."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.4","order":"02.40.001.63374"},["b","4"],"Whereas Edom saith, We are impoverished, but we will return and build the desolate places; thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, They shall build, but I will throw down; and they shall call them, The border of wickedness, and, The people against whom the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath indignation for ever."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.5","order":"02.40.001.63375"},["b","5"],"And your eyes shall see, and ye shall say, The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"will be magnified from the border of Israel."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.6","order":"02.40.001.63376"},["b","6"],"¶A son",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"honoureth"],["i","his"],"father, and a servant his master: if then I",["i","be"],"a father, where",["i","is"],"mine",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"honour"],"? and if I",["i","be"],"a master, where",["i","is"],"my fear? saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts unto you, O priests, that despise my name. And ye say, Wherein have we despised thy name?"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.7","order":"02.40.001.63377"},["b","7"],"Ye offer polluted bread upon mine altar; and ye say, Wherein have we polluted thee? In that ye say, The table of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],"contemptible."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.8","order":"02.40.001.63378"},["b","8"],"And if ye offer the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"blind"],"for",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"sacrifice"],",",["i","is it"],"not evil? and if ye offer",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"the lame and sick"],",",["i","is it"],"not evil? offer it now unto thy governor; will he be pleased with thee, or accept thy person? saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.9","order":"02.40.001.63379"},["b","9"],"And now, I pray you, beseech God that he will be gracious unto us: this hath been by your means: will he regard your persons? saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.10","order":"02.40.001.63380"},["b","10"],"Who",["i","is there"],"even among you that would shut the doors",["i","for nought?"],"neither do ye kindle",["i","fire"],"on mine altar for nought. I have no pleasure in you, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, neither will I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"accept"],"an offering at your hand."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.11","order":"02.40.001.63381"},["b","11"],"For from the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"rising"],"of the sun even unto the going down of the same my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"name"],["i","shall be"],"great among the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"Gentiles"],"; and in every place incense",["i","shall be"],"offered unto my name, and a pure offering: for my name",["i","shall be"],"great among the heathen, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.12","order":"02.40.001.63382"},["b","12"],"¶But ye have profaned it, in that ye say, The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"table"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],"polluted; and the fruit thereof,",["i","even"],"his meat,",["i","is"],"contemptible."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.13","order":"02.40.001.63383"},["b","13"],"Ye said also, Behold, what a weariness",["i","is it!"],"and ye have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"snuffed at it"],", saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts; and ye brought",["i","that which was"],"torn, and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"lame"],", and the sick; thus ye brought an offering: should I",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"accept"],"this of your hand? saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.14","order":"02.40.001.63384"},["b","14"],"But",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"cursed"],["i","be"],"the deceiver, which hath in his flock a male, and voweth, and sacrificeth unto the Lord a corrupt thing: for I",["i","am"],"a great King, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, and my name",["i","is"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"dreadful"],"among the heathen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.1a","order":"02.40.001.63385"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-keys-of"},"TG Priesthood, Keys of"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.2a","order":"02.40.001.63387"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-love-of"},"TG God, Love of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/love"},"Love"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.2b","order":"02.40.001.63389"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/9.13"},"Rom. 9:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.3a","order":"02.40.001.63391"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.10"},"Jer. 49:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.3b","order":"02.40.001.63393"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/25.13"},"Ezek. 25:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.3c","order":"02.40.001.63395"},["b","3c"],["span.small","HEB"],"jackals."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.6a","order":"02.40.001.63397"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-children-duties-of"},"TG Family, Children, Duties of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.6b","order":"02.40.001.63399"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/honoring-father-and-mother"},"TG Honoring Father and Mother"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.8a","order":"02.40.001.63401"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/22.22"},"Lev. 22:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.8b","order":"02.40.001.63403"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sacrifice"},"TG Sacrifice"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.8c","order":"02.40.001.63405"},["b","8c"],["span.small","IE"],"lame or sick animals."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.10a","order":"02.40.001.63407"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.22.21-22"},"Amos 5:22 (21–22)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/9.19.19-20"},"3 Ne. 9:19 (19–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.11a","order":"02.40.001.63409"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/45.6"},"Isa. 45:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.11b","order":"02.40.001.63411"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/59.19"},"Isa. 59:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/2.11"},"Zeph. 2:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/2.9.5-12"},"Philip. 2:9 (5–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/18.23.21-25"},"D&C 18:23 (21–25)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.104"},"88:104"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.11c","order":"02.40.001.63413"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/56.7"},"Isa. 56:7"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/gentiles"},"TG Gentiles"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.12a","order":"02.40.001.63415"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.22"},"Ezek. 41:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/44.16"},"44:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.13a","order":"02.40.001.63417"},["b","13a"],["span.small","OR"],"belittled it."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.13b","order":"02.40.001.63419"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/22.22.22-25"},"Lev. 22:22 (22–25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.13c","order":"02.40.001.63421"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/22.20"},"Lev. 22:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.14a","order":"02.40.001.63423"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/curse"},"TG Curse"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/mal/1.14b","order":"02.40.001.63425"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.70.70-75"},"D&C 45:70 (70–75)"],"."]]}
